string.name: oobe_rcs_enhanced_service_message_new_4g
string.value: [TS_870541]_Advanced Messaging lets you send and receive messages and multimedia content (such as images, voice messages, and locations) using WLAN or mobile data. During use, your device version and identifiers (including IMEI, IMSI, MSISDN, and WLAN MAC address) will be sent to your carrier, who provides this service. You can change your settings at any time in Messaging > More > Settings > Advanced Messaging. For information about usage fees, please contact your carrier. This service will read the list of installed apps on your device and check the login statuses of third-party Advanced Messaging apps in order to ensure that this service works properly. By turning on the switch, you agree to let us provide you with this service.
